 Wasser ist wertvoll – und je sparsamer wir damit umgehen, desto besser.“</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></article></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1773666101233" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1773666101233" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/479e4a06-af0b-4473-ac5c-0ee784dd8d32/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/17.png" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" width="1920" height="1080" natural-width="1920" natural-height="1080"></div></div><div data-label="Button" data-key="button" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996390" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-gpicon-button" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709026996390"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-stretch-lg="0" data-stretch-md="0" data-stretch-sm="0" data-stretch-xs="0"><a class="button btn gf_button gf_gs-button-element gf_gs-button---large" href="https://gartenort.de/products/ultrawasher" target="" data-scroll-speed="2000" data-exc="" data-scroll-speed-md="2000" data-scroll-speed-sm="2000" data-scroll-speed-xs="2000" aria-describedby="a11y-external-message"><span>Jetzt Rabatt und Verfügbarkeit prüfen ➡️</span></a></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709026996333" class="gf_row gf_equal-height gf_row-gap-10" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709026996333" data-layout-lg="12" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;" data-row-gap="10px"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1685516813895" data-id="1685516813895" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset;